Probably my favorite restaurant in the Burbank area. The food is consistently excellent, and the desserts and coffee are equally good. My personal favorites are the chicken kebab plate and the chicken wrap. A great spot for a full meal or even just coffee and dessert. Highly recommend.
Amazing food
